route_description: Renton Highlands - Renton TC
reasons: It’s one of the lower performing routes in Metro’s system, and there is alternative service available for most riders.

In Maplewood, Metro’s RideShare or VanPool programs may be options.

route_description: Kennydale - Renton TC
reasons: It’s one of the lowest performing routes in Metro’s system.
rider_options:
In the Renton Highlands near Group Health and the Renton Technical College, use revised Route 105.
In the Renton Highlands near NE Sunset Boulevard, use revised Route 240.
In Kennydale, use Sound Transit Route 560 at the NE 30th Street/I-405 Freeway Stop.
In the Kennydale DART service area, Metro’s RideShare or VanPool programs may be options.
